Package com.pandora.general.objects.builders

Class PandoraTimestepBuilder

java.lang.Object
com.pandora.general.objects.builders.PandoraTimestepBuilder
public class PandoraTimestepBuilder extends Object
The PandoraTimestepBuilder class is a builder for creating instances of PandoraTimestep. It provides methods to set various parameters such as initial values, time step duration, dimensionality, discharge, volume, and arrays of terrestrial and upstream sources. It follows the builder pattern, allowing for a flexible and readable way to construct instances of PandoraTimestep.
Version:
0.0.1
Author:
Wim Joost van Hoek
